'''CoruFresh Farm Produce''' was a [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]-based company that supplied fresh [[Fruit/Legends|fruit]] and [[Vegetable/Legends|vegetables]]. Its main distribution division was in [[Quadrant F-76]] on Coruscant. This was the location of a major anti-terrorism operation by [[Omega Squad|Omega]] and [[Delta Squad/Legends|Delta]] Squads, 385 days after the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|First Battle of Geonosis]].

